Signal is the leader in cross channel marketing technology, allowing customers to own their marketing data in real time, while making it actionable across their current partners


##### Integration
Optimizely's integration with Signal TMS allows customers to easily and effectively pass data to their partners in real-time, reducing the number of tags on their site and stopping data loss. Customers only need to implement one piece of code into the footer of their site in order to pass data to their partners.
